Articles.Content:
Sorry if this was the wrong spot to put this but after watching Capt'n Skunky's videos I can't help but wonder what mods he currently is using. To be more specific the ones in http://www.twitch.tv/kerbalsp/b/401805676

Any help as to identify what mods these are would be greatly appreciated. Would love to give these a go and see what I can come up with.
Subassmaly, KSPX, KW Rocketry, Mechjeb, NovaPunch, HOME mod, TT modular wheels, Fairing factory, and some other mods I don't recognize.
All great mods. I recommend you try them out, they add some really cool and useful stuff.
